---
---

<section id="nosotros" class="about" aria-label="Sobre DUXER">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <!-- Left: Text -->
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <h2 class="about-heading">
        Tu garantía<br />
        en atención<br />
        y calidad
      </h2>

      <div class="about-divider"></div>

      <p class="about-body">
        Como empresa orgullosamente argentina, en DUXER brindamos equipos de
        lavandería industrial que combinan calidad, accesibilidad y servicio
        excepcional.
      </p>

      <p class="about-body">
        Ofrecemos soluciones completas que respalden el desempeño y la
        continuidad de tu operación.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Real photo of industrial washing machines -->
    <div class="about-image">
      <img
        src="/lavandery.png"
        alt="Equipos de lavandería industrial DUXER — fila de lavadoras de barrera sanitaria"
        width="700"
        height="550"
        loading="lazy"
        class="about-img"
      />
      <div class="about-img-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: #080808;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 520px;
  }

  .about-text {
    padding: 5rem clamp(2rem, 4vw, 5rem);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-heading {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    color: white;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .about-divider {
    width: 36px;
    height: 2px;
    background: rgba(200, 168, 107, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 380px;
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    min-height: 440px;
  }

  /* Subtle left fade so it blends with the text panel */
  .about-img-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      rgba(8, 8, 8, 0.55) 0%,
      transparent 40%
    );
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .about-image {
      order: -1;
      height: 260px;
    }
    .about-img {
      min-height: 260px;
    }
    .about-text {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
